title: KEY Crosses Above Key Moving Average Level - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Thursday, shares of KeyCorp (Symbol: KEY) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $16.81, changing hands as high as $17.18 per share. KeyCorp shares are currently trading up about 4.4% on the day. The chart below shows the one year performance of KEY shares, versus its 200 day moving average:     Looking at the chart above, KEY's low point in its 52 week range is $13.655 per share, with $21.371 as the 52 week high point - that compares with a last trade of $17.13.
